AASSKKCCCC -- Environmental Variable

Force prompting for CC names
AASSKKCCCC=_Y_E_S/_N_O

The environmental  variable AASSKKCCCC  directs the  program mmaaiill to  prompt for
carbon-copy names.  A carbon-copy (or CC) name gives another person to whom
a mail message should be sent.  To turn on prompting, use the command:

    export ASKCC=YES

_S_e_e _A_l_s_o
eennvviirroonnmmeennttaall vvaarriiaabblleess, mmaaiill
